rows.label: tlk41700222_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Since I spend all my time chopping
down trees, I'm not exactly sensitive
to the ways of the wider world.

rows.label: tlk41700222_01_msg0002
rows.name:
But I know the craftsmen in Torigo
turn the trees I fell into gorgeous pieces
of furniture or musical instruments.

rows.label: tlk41700222_01_msg0003
rows.name:
And the things they craft go on to
make all sorts of customers happy.

rows.label: tlk41700222_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Isn't that enough, when it comes
right down to it?

rows.label: tlk41700222_01_msg0005
rows.name:
That's why no matter what happens,
I'm just gonna stay right here, chopping
down these here trees.
